Snake Evolution – Modern Snake Game in Python 🎮

Snake Evolution is a modern, GUI-based version of the classic Snake game — built entirely in Python with Pygame.
It features smooth animations, an interactive main menu, glowing visuals, and dynamic gameplay that speeds up as your snake grows!

🚀 Features

🎨 Stylish Front Menu with animated background and buttons

🧠 Smart Gameplay – snake wraps around the screen edges

⚡ Speed Increases as you eat more food

🏆 High Score System (saved locally)

⏸️ Pause / Resume / Restart options

📱 Mobile-like interface with smooth UI transitions
